这里有几条指令：testfor @e ItemFrame {Item:"minecraft:stone"}
testfor @e[-127,12,31,0,type=ItemFrame] {Item:"minecraft:stone"}
testfor @e[-127,12,31,0,type=ItemFrame] {TileEntityData:{Items:"minecraft:stone"}}复制代码请问哪几条指令才对？如果都不对的话，请问怎么检验某个指定坐标的展示框内是否有某物品？ 还有，请问这条指令是什么意思？<FONT size=2 face=Verdana>scoreboard players set @e[type=ItemFrame] spi 0 {ItemRotation:0b}</FONT>复制代码
